data.description: Welcome Home to 5913 Weymouth St.  This beautiful Property is located in the Lawncrest Section of Northeast Philadelphia.  This home is Gorgeous!!!  As walk up to the front of this property you will notice the nice and beautiful curb appeal with beautiful and awesome sized awnings and an awesome sized front cemented patio area and a gardening area to grow your beautiful flowers or Etc.  As you walk through the front door you will notice the awesome sized enclosed front porch/sunroom area with beautiful floors, great lighting and plenty of nice windows to let the sunlight into the home.  The living room is nice and spacious and features nice hardwood floors, recess lighting, nice and neutral paint colors. There is an awesome sized dining room area to have your awesome family dinners and features awesome hardwood floors, nice chandelier lighting, nice & neutral paint colors. And a half bathroom for your convenience. As you walk into this amazing awesome sized updated eat-in kitchen you will notice the awesome tiled flooring, nice lighting, beautiful kitchen cabinets with plenty of cabinet space, awesome styled granite counter tops with awesome counter space with beautiful back splash, a deep stainless-steel sink with an awesome kitchen sink faucet, Gas Stove, Built in Microwave, Dishwasher and beautiful windows for that awesome sunlight to come into the home.  You will also notice the door off of the kitchen that will lead you onto the nice shared little deck.  As you walk up to the 2nd floor you will notice the nice hardwood stairs and the spacious hallway with beautiful hardwood flooring.  You will then notice that the 2nd floor features 3 awesome size bedrooms with an awesome full hall bathroom.  The master bedroom is Large with great closet space & beautiful hardwood flooring, neutral paint colors, and a nice ceiling fan with lighting. The middle bedroom is a good size with good closet space, beautiful hardwood flooring, neutral paint colors, and a nice light fixture.  The back bedroom is an awesome size with good size closet space, beautiful hardwood flooring, neutral paint colors, and a nice light fixture.  There is an awesome sized beautiful, titled hall bathroom that is nice and clean and features an awesome sized mirror and lighting with a nice sink & faucet, nice dual flush Toilet and a beautiful size Jacuzzi Tub for you to relax in or you can use the awesome shower and features an awesome skylight.  There is a nice spacious Full & Finished basement with awesome ceiling height and has awesome possibilities to turn into a 4th bedroom or an office area. This basement also has a full bathroom with a stall shower for your convenience and a nice laundry area.  The basement area also features a door that will lead you into the nice one car garage area with inside access or you can go through the other door from the basement that will lead you to the rear of the property out to the rear driveway area.  Also, the Front Storm Door was replaced in 9/2023.  The awnings were installed approximately 2 years ago.  And the kitchen was updated in 9/2023.  As you can see this home has been very well kept & cared for. You will have to see this home to appreciate it. This home is a great buy and as a new homeowner YOU will enjoy your new home and all of the features of this home. Why Rent a Home when you can buy this Home Today.  It's within walking distance to public transportation, Schools, Shopping and much more. This home is a Must See. Just pack your bags and move right in.  Schedule your appointment Today!
